        <h1 class = "bigTitleFont-black"><strong> <center> THE APPLICATION PROCESS   </center></strong> </h1>
    <h3 class = "applyText"> Our application is designed to ensure that students involved meet the academic prerequisites to apply to top tier universities while maintaining unique interests, ambition and intellectual curiosity that are aimed at making an impact in the future. Our judgements will be made in context of applicant age and location. In the simplest sense, we are looking for people that stand out amongst their peers for their academic and extracurricular performance.
