  <li>Do you believe that you belong in a top tier university? </li>
  <li>Do you feel that you will benefit from gaining first hand information from those who study at a particular university? </li>
  <li>Is there more that you can do to achieve your academic, extracurricular and application related goals? </li>
</ul>

<br>
